Suzanne Bofia (amụrụ na Nọvemba 9, 1984 na Bafia, Cameroon) bụ onye Cameroon kọlejị basketball player, onye bụbu onye otu Mahadum Arizona
Ọ bụ nwanne ejima nke onye otu Wildcats bụ Beatrice Bofia.
N'afọ 2006-07, Bofia nwetara akara 4.4 na 3.4 rebounds kwa egwuregwu na oge mbụ ya na Arizona mgbe ọ hapụsịrị Illinois Central College.
